4 ending on or prior to June 30, 2033, Twenty Million Dollars
5 ($20,000,000.00) per fiscal year for the construction, repair, and
6 maintenance of weigh stations on the state highway system.
7 E. From the monies allocated pursuant to the provisions of
8 subparagraph a of paragraph 1 of subsection B of this section each
9 fiscal year, the Department of Transportation shall make payments
10 required for the payment of principal, interest, and other costs
11 related to the obligations issued by the Oklahoma Capitol
