13 341 151 et seq. of Title 73 of the Oklahoma Statutes, Section 350 of
14 Title 73 of the Oklahoma Statutes and Section 1 of Enrolled House
15 Bill No. 2896 of the 1st Session of the 58th Oklahoma Legislature,
16 and such payments shall be made by the Department each fiscal year
17 before such monies are used for any other purpose.
18 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
19 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
20 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
21 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
22 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
